Package org.soulwing.prospecto.runtime.accessor

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Accessor
    An accessor for a property of a model.
    AccessorBuilder
    A factory that produces an Accessor.
    AccessorBuilderFactory
    A factory that produces AccessorBuilder objects.
    AccessorFactory
    A factory that produces Accessor objects.
    IndexedMultiValuedAccessor
    A MultiValuedAccessor that supports an ordered collection that allows duplicates.
    MultiValuedAccessor
    An accessor for a multi-valued property such as an array or a collection.
    MultiValuedAccessorFactory
    A factory that produces MultiValuedAccessor objects.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractAccessor
    An abstract base for Accessor implementations.
    ArrayAccessor
    An accessor for the elements of an array.
    CollectionAccessor
    An accessor for the elements of a collection.
    ConcreteMultiValuedAccessorFactory
    A MultiValuedAccessorFactory implementation.
    ListAccessor
    A MultiValuedAccessor for a List.
    ReflectionAccessorBuilderFactory
    An AccessorBuilderFactory that produces ReflectionAccessorBuilder objects.
    ReflectionAccessorFactory
    An AccessorFactory that produces accessors using the Reflection API.
    RootAccessor
    An accessor for a root object.
